OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,FJersey Electricity's (JE) CEO says a
OL,7,Fground-mount solar panel installation
OL,8,Fon the island will help reduce energy
OL,9,Fprices in the long term.
OL,11,FChris Ambler told ITV News that the
OL,12,F4.3 MegaWatt installation in St
OL,13,FClement would help Jersey diversify
OL,14,Fits energy production methods and
OL,15,Freduce its reliance on imported power.
OL,17,FMr Ambler said: "One of the challenges
OL,18,Fthat we have with these sorts of
OL,19,Fdevelopments is that the cost of the
OL,20,Fenergy produced is still higher than
OL,21,Fimporting from France.
