OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,F"However, the strategy is to get into
OL,7,Fthis area of project, drive the cost
OL,8,Fdown and make it more economically
OL,9,Fviable vis-a-vis imported power."
OL,11,FThe JE boss says that if similar
OL,12,Fdevelopments are built in other parts
OL,13,Fof the island, then the price of
OL,14,Felectricity produced by solar panels
OL,15,Fis more likely to come down.
OL,17,FJE currently has two other sites in
OL,18,FJersey earmarked for ground-mounted
OL,19,Fsolar energy production and is also
OL,20,Fworking on installing more roof-based
OL,21,Fsolar panels across the island.
