OL,6,FEarlier this week, JE increased
OL,7,Fislanders' electricity tariff by 7.5%
OL,8,Ffrom January 2025, adding around #2
OL,9,Fextra per week to the average
OL,10,Fhousehold bill.
OL,12,FThe company blamed higher-than-normal
OL,13,Fwholesale energy prices for the hike.
OL,15,FMr Ambler says that while the
OL,16,F"community-based" solar development in
OL,17,FSt Clement is a step in the right
OL,18,Fdirection toward driving down consumer
OL,19,Fprices, it is not an easy fix.
