OL,3,CGround-mounted solar farm in Jersey
OL,4,Ccould drive down energy prices
OL,6,FHe said: "There's no golden nugget
OL,7,Fsolution here. What we're trying to do
OL,8,Fis to develop a package of solutions
OL,9,Fand they all have a role at a level.
OL,11,F"One of the other really important
OL,12,Fthings about this development is that
OL,13,Fit is, in a sense, temporary.
OL,15,F"Yes, it's got a 40-year life, but at
OL,16,Fthe end of that 40-year period we can
OL,17,Fremove the solar panels and we can
OL,18,Frestore the site to bare earth."
